---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Base title="Author Record – LexBlog Library" description="Get an Author Record to tie your full body of work to one verified identity. Your publishing becomes citable across HeinOnline, vLex/Clio, and LLMs." currentPage="author-record">
  <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 pt-9 pb-24">
    {/* Breadcrumb */}
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[12px] leading-5 mb-[30px]">
      <a href="/" class="text-neutral-400 no-underline">LexBlog</a>
      <span class="text-stone-300">/</span>
      <a href="/" class="text-neutral-400 no-underline">Library</a>
      <span class="text-stone-300">/</span>
      <span class="text-zinc-900 font-medium">Author Record</span>
    </div>

    {/* Title */}
    <h1 class="m-0 text-[32px] md:text-[46px] font-[800] leading-[1.05] text-neutral-950">Get an Author Record</h1>

    {/* Subtitle */}
    <p class="mt-6 mb-0 text-[20px] md:text-[24px] font-semibold leading-[1.4] text-neutral-950">
      Your work counts. Make it recognized, and make it last.
    </p>

    {/* Intro */}
    <p class="mt-3.5 mb-0 max-w-[760px] text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.65] text-zinc-600">
      Submitting your work is free. An Author Record is how you support the Library that preserves it, and how you secure verified authority over your own body of work.
    </p>

    {/* Dark card */}
    <div class="mt-9 bg-neutral-950 rounded-2xl px-7 md:px-11 pt-8 md:pt-10 pb-8 md:pb-9">
      <p class="m-0 text-white text-[18px] md:text-[22px] font-semibold leading-[1.45]">
        With an Author Record, your publishing establishes your authority for the legal research platforms (HeinOnline, vLex/Clio, and others) and LLMs, and your publishing becomes citable.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-5 mb-0 text-zinc-400 text-[16px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.55]">
        These platforms already receive Library publishing, with more partners coming.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Ten fields label */}
    <div class="mt-12 mb-5">
      <span class="text-neutral-400 text-[12px] font-medium font-mono uppercase leading-5 tracking-[0.15em]">Each record contains ten fields</span>
    </div>

    {/* Fields table */}
    <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
        {[
          ["Photo", "Authorized name"],
          ["Firm or organization", "Practice areas"],
          ["Jurisdictions", "Law school"],
          ["Bar admissions", "Professional bio"],
          ["Author Record ID", "Link to complete body of work"],
        ].map(([left, right], i) => (
          <>
            <div class:list={[
              "px-6 py-5 text-[15px] md:text-base text-zinc-900 leading-6 border-b border-gray-200",
              "md:border-r"
            ]}>
              {left}
            </div>
            <div class:list={[
              "px-6 py-5 text-[15px] md:text-base text-zinc-900 leading-6",
              i < 4 ? "border-b border-gray-200" : "",
              "max-md:border-b max-md:border-gray-200"
            ]}>
              {right}
            </div>
          </>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Pricing cards */}
    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
      {/* Monthly */}
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 px-7 pt-7 pb-8 flex flex-col">
        <span class="text-neutral-400 text-[12px] font-medium font-mono uppercase leading-5 tracking-[0.15em]">Monthly</span>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline">
          <span class="text-neutral-950 text-[44px] md:text-[48px] font-[800] leading-[1]">$19</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-400 text-[18px] leading-7 ml-1">/month</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href="https://www.lexblog.com/wp-json/lxb_profiles/v1/profileSignup?user_id=0&billing_frequency=monthly" class="flex items-center justify-center h-14 bg-white rounded-lg border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-900 text-base font-semibold leading-6 no-underline hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors">
            Choose monthly
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Annual */}
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border-2 border-neutral-950 px-7 pt-7 pb-8 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="text-neutral-400 text-[12px] font-medium font-mono uppercase leading-5 tracking-[0.15em]">Annual</span>
          <span class="bg-neutral-950 text-white text-[12px] font-semibold leading-5 px-3 py-[5px] rounded-[20px]">Save $29</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline">
          <span class="text-neutral-950 text-[44px] md:text-[48px] font-[800] leading-[1]">$199</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-400 text-[18px] leading-7 ml-1">/year</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href="https://www.lexblog.com/wp-json/lxb_profiles/v1/profileSignup?user_id=0&billing_frequency=yearly" class="flex items-center justify-center h-14 bg-neutral-950 rounded-lg text-white text-base font-semibold leading-6 no-underline hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors">
            Choose annual
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Contact line */}
    <div class="mt-10 pt-7 border-t border-gray-200">
      <p class="m-0 text-zinc-600 text-[15px] md:text-base leading-7">
        For law firms with multiple authors, please contact the Library at LexBlog at
        <a href="tel:1-800-913-0988" class="text-zinc-900 underline underline-offset-2">1-800-913-0988</a> or
        <a href="mailto:library@lexblog.com" class="text-zinc-900 underline underline-offset-2">library@lexblog.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
